                        <interp inst="t18491126-name-187" type="given" value="SARAH MARY"></interp>SARAH MARY ORPWOOD</persName>
                  </hi>. On 16th Nov., the prisoner came to me and asked for a shilling Prayer-book, and offered me a five-shilling-piece—I said 1 did not think it was good—he said, "I hope it is, for I have just got it in change for a half-sovereign, in the City-road"—I took it to my husband.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
