                  </hi>. I am the husband of the last witness. She gave me a crown in the prisoner's presence—I tried it with aquafortis, and found it was bad—I told the prisoner so, and asked where he lived—he said in Oxford-street—the crown was given to Enright in my presence.</p>
               <p>
